 {"title": "Coaching capabilities are minimal", "detail": "There are no structured coaching scorecards or systematic call review workflows comparable to Gong. Managers can watch recordings and leave comments, but the tooling doesn't support building a scalable coaching program. Teams with 20+ reps that need data-driven coaching should look at dedicated CI tools."},
 {"title": "Limited deal intelligence and pipeline integration", "detail": "Avoma's CRM integration pushes meeting data to Salesforce and HubSpot, but it doesn't provide the pipeline risk scoring, multi-threading analysis, or forecast signals that Gong offers. Revenue leaders who want conversation signals feeding into pipeline management won't get that from Avoma without supplementing it with another tool."},
